com.aventstack.extentreports

Interface TestListener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExtentReporter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractReporter, BasicFileReporter, ConfigurableReporter, ConsoleLogger, ExtentAventReporter, ExtentBDDReporter, ExtentCardsReporter, ExtentEmailReporter, ExtentHtmlReporter, ExtentKlovReporter, ExtentLoggerReporter, ExtentTabularReporter

    public interface TestListener
    Listener methods invoked when an event occurs in the report:
    • A test or node is started
    • A category or author is added
    • A media object is added etc.
